{"tid":617253,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"認真討論: 眾籌買地起樓!","createTime":"2018-04-04T20:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T21:25:33.000Z","uid":65690,"like":81,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"94f2ad82f9a9b930eae2edf11b3b364e74d957c6","tid":617253,"uid":65690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T20:30:31.000Z","msg":"可能我上一個po開錯台或者講得比較模糊，所以無咩人理，於是決定係到再開過!<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價點解顛價？仲要咁都仲有人肯買，有錢買黎炒個d吹佢唔漲，但普通人就因為咁要付出三四十年去養層蚊型樓，當你30歲開始供，60，70歲先供完，癡左線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網搵過地產商賣樓利潤有成20%-30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/041841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F041841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66d399d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係一層600萬既樓地產商賺120萬-180萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與其比地產奸商榨到盡，點解唔行多步，用我地既血汗錢買地起樓!!!!!!!!等班pk地產商食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一個po有人提到之前有人咁做成功左，不過利潤太高所以違背左眾籌既原意，做埋pk地產商個份。有見及此，如果真係搞得成，眾籌之時要簽訂一份協議，我地起出黎既樓唔可以轉手炒賣，只供自住!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設有1萬個人夾錢，每人10萬，<br />\n已經有1 000 000 000!!!!!!!<br />\n起一萬個單位如何？<br />\n<br />\n你或者覺得我發緊夢，但當政垃圾政府都做唔到野既時候，就只可以靠自己! 點知唔會有實現既一日? 所謂星星之火可以燎原，如果唔止我一個覺得做得到，咁件事就好可能成真! 打倒地產霸權指日可待!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你同我發緊同一個夢，請留低一個正評，令呢個夢成真!<br />\n<br />\np.s. 如果可以，好想買埋南生圍塊地黎植樹，令佢變返以前咁，甚至更好! 防火搶地正pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8e7b2bec9d98dc6e5ccac10a600bc5359edc59","tid":617253,"uid":65690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T20:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能我上一個po開錯台或者講得比較模糊，所以無咩人理，於是決定係到再開過!<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價點解顛價？仲要咁都仲有人肯買，有錢買黎炒個d吹佢唔漲，但普通人就因為咁要付出三四十年去養層蚊型樓，當你30歲開始供，60，70歲先供完，癡左線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網搵過地產商賣樓利潤有成20%-30%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/05/041841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2F041841_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=66d399d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係一層600萬既樓地產商賺120萬-180萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n與其比地產奸商榨到盡，點解唔行多步，用我地既血汗錢買地起樓!!!!!!!!等班pk地產商食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一個po有人提到之前有人咁做成功左，不過利潤太高所以違背左眾籌既原意，做埋pk地產商個份。有見及此，如果真係搞得成，眾籌之時要簽訂一份協議，我地起出黎既樓唔可以轉手炒賣，只供自住!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設有1萬個人夾錢，每人10萬，<br />\n已經有1 000 000 000!!!