解唔行多步，用我地既血汗錢買地起樓!!!!!!!!等班pk地產商食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一個po有人提到之前有人咁做成功左，不過利潤太高所以違背左眾籌既原意，做埋pk地產商個份。有見及此，如果真係搞得成，眾籌之時要簽訂一份協議，我地起出黎既樓唔可以轉手炒賣，只供自住!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假設有1萬個人夾錢，每人10萬，<br />\n已經有1 000 000 000!!!!!!!<br />\n起一萬個單位如何？<br />\n<br />\n你或者覺得我發緊夢，但當政垃圾政府都做唔到野既時候，就只可以靠自己! 點知唔會有實現既一日? 所謂星星之火可以燎原，如果唔止我一個覺得做得到，咁件事就好可能成真! 打倒地產霸權指日可待!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你同我發緊同一個夢，請留低一個正評，令呢個夢成真!<br />\n<br />\np.s. 如果可以，好想買埋南生圍塊地黎植樹，令佢變返以前咁，甚至更好! 防火搶地正pk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T10:00:57.000Z","msg":"妳唔會聯手比人打壓? 由工人，水泥 鋼根  每樣野都比大地產商出手打壓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"最大鑊係呢度，唔知有冇法律可以保障？"},{"pid":"b3f485775c2a80038f7bb9e91d147e141148d5a2","tid":617253,"uid":48139,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"Design 同 planning自己無相關知識點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有野判晒俾街外做會唔會仲貴?"},{"pid":"c8b7cadd52f669cc7195601c19d8a74e6f0aa82a","tid":617253,"uid":104900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"94f2ad82f9a9b930eae2edf11b3b364e74d957c6","tid":617253,"uid":65690,"like":0